Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.95,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's true that any kind of wish can be granted, right?{本当に、どんな願いでも叶うんだね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:19.95,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Your prayer can undoubtedly be accomplished.{大丈夫、君の祈りは間違いなく遂げられる}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.52,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Well then... it's okay, right?{じゃあ、いいんだね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.29,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Do it.{うん、やって}{she sounds like hirano aya here}
