Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.55,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Ah, how improper.{あ、はしたない}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.30,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon.{ごめんあそばせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.80,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hitomi?{どうしたのよ仁美}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.68,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Lack of sleep?{寝不足？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:48.14,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yes. Last night, I was at the hospital and with the police until late into the evening...{ええ、昨夜は病院やら警察やらで夜遅くまで}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.23,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Ehh? Did something happen?{えー、何かあったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.48,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I was sleepwalking or something...{何だか私、夢遊病っていうのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.73,Madoka,,0,0,0,,And there were a lot of people with the same type of symptoms.{それも同じような症状の方が大勢いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:00.15,Madoka,,0,0,0,,When I regained consciousness, everyone was lying in the same place.{気がついたら、みんなで同じ場所に倒れていたんですの}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.28,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?{何それ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:06.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Doctor-sama said it was a mass hallucination or something.{お医者様は集団幻覚だとか何とか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.71,Madoka,,0,0,0,,And today, I need to have a detailed examination after school as a result.{今日も放課後に精密検査に行かなくてはなりませんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.58,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Such a bother.{面倒くさいわ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.59,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, it would have been fine to take a break from school!{そんな事なら、学校休んじゃえばいいのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:19.67,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't do! Then, it'd seem as if I was truly ill.{ダメですわ。それではまるで本当に病気みたいで}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.59,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It would create more and more worry for the people at home.{家の者がますます心配してしまいますもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.68,Madoka,,0,0,0,,As expected of an honor student!{さっすが優等生}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Admirable!{偉いわー}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.11,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I haven't felt this good in a long time!{久々に気分良いわー}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.03,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Refreshing, refreshing!{爽快爽快}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.45,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan... aren't you scared?{さやかちゃんはさ、怖くはないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.95,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hmm? That is, I'm a little scared, but...{ん？そりゃあちょっとは怖いけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.62,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Well, the one from yesterday was an easy victory, after all.{まぁ、昨日の奴にはあっさり勝てたし}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If by some chance... Madoka and Hitomi.{もしかしたらまどかと仁美}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:58.63,Madoka,,0,0,0,,The possibility that I may have lost two of my friends simultaneously...{友達二人も同時に亡くしてかもしれないって}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That outcome is much scarier, you know.{そっちの方がよっぽど怖いよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,So...{だ～か～ら～}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.29,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I wonder what to call it... confidence?{何つーかな。自信？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.89,Madoka,,0,0,0,,A feeling of relief?{安心感？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.48,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel like praising myself a little bit, you know.{ちょっと自分を褒めちゃいたい気分っつーかね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.02,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Well...{まー}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.98,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'm soaring high, you know!{舞い上がっちゃってますね、私}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.11,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Because from now on, Mitakihara City's peace...{これからのミタキハラ市の平和は}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:24.99,Madoka,,0,0,0,,will be passionately protected by this "Magical Girl Sayaka-chan" here, after all!{この魔法少女さやかちゃんが、ガンガン守りまくっちゃいますからねー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.12,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You don't have any regrets or anything at all?{後悔とか全然ないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.87,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Well, right... If I had to name a regret...{そうねー。後悔って言えば}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.37,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hesitating would be my regret, I guess.{迷ってたことが後悔かな}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:41.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If I was going to do it regardless, I'd say I should have made up my mind a little bit sooner.{どうせだったらもうちょっと早く心を決めるべきだったなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.02,Madoka,,0,0,0,,The witch at that time...{あの時の魔女}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:48.72,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If we had both fought it together... for all I know, that may have prevented Mami-san's death.{私と二人がかりで戦ってたら、マミさんも死なないで済んだかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.18,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I...{私}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.28,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hey now, you're thinking of something weird, aren't you?{さーてーは、何か変な事考えてるなー？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.53,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I... If I had...{私、私だって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.66,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I can say these things since it's after I've become one.{なっちゃった後だから言えるの、こういう事は}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.60,Madoka,,0,0,0,,The key point is that I did it regardless.{どうせならって言うのがミソなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You know, this means that as long as it was possible, I would have become a magical girl.{私はさ、成るべくして魔法少女になったわけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.25,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan...{さやかちゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.17,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I found... something to wish for.{願い事、見つけたんだもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:29.43,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It appears I had something that I didn't mind risking my life to fight for.{命懸けで戦うハメになったって構わないって、そう思えるだけの理由があったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.43,Madoka,,0,0,0,,The fact that I was so slow to realize it...{そう気付くのが遅すぎたって言うのが}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.64,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Frustrates me a little, that's all.{ちょっと悔しいだけでさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.64,Madoka,,0,0,0,,So, it's fine if you don't feel weak or anything like that.{だから引け目なんて感じなくていいんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:45.18,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It means you don't have to end up becoming a magical girl, Madoka.{まどかは魔法少女にならずに済んだって言う}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.03,Madoka,,0,0,0,,And it means nothing more than simply that.{ただそれだけの事なんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.45,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah...{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.58,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Well now... I need to get going soon, then.{さてと、じゃあ私はそろそろ行かないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Do you have something to do?{何か用事があるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.42,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Well, a bit, you know.{まあ、ちょっとね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.30,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I see... you haven't been discharged yet, then.{そっか、退院はまだなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.43,Madoka,,0,0,0,,The rehabilitation for my legs still hasn't been completed.{足のリハビリが、まだ済んでないしね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:11.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I need to be able to properly walk first, after all...{ちゃんと、歩けるようになってからでないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:17.52,Madoka,,0,0,0,,As for my hand, they say that they have absolutely no idea why it just healed...{手の方も、一体どうして急に治ったのか、まったく理由がわからないんだってさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.98,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's why they're going to closely examine it for a little while longer.{だから、もうしばらく精密検査がいるんだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.29,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke, how's your self-confidence?{恭介自信はどうなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.74,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Does any part of your body feel strange?{どっか身体におかしなとこ、ある？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No... it's so normal, you could call it scary.{いや、なさ過ぎて怖いっていうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:36.25,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's like everything after the accident was just a bad dream.{事故に遭ったのさえ悪い夢だったみたいに思えてくる}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.75,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I wonder, "Why am I lying in this bed?"{何で僕、こんなベッドに寝てるのかなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.50,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Exactly like you said, Sayaka... This is a miracle, isn't it?{さやかが言った通り、奇跡だよね、これ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:54.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka, I said awful things to you, didn't I?{さやかには…ひどいこと言っちゃったよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:56.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No matter how depressed how I was, I shouldn't have.{いくら気が滅入ってたとはいえ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:58.80,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you don't remember anything weird!{変な事思い出さなくていいの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:02.06,Madoka,,0,0,0,,After all, it's natural for you to be overjoyed right now, Kyousuke!{今の恭介は大喜びして当然なんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.40,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Don't make a face like that.{そんな顔しちゃだめだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.96,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.90,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Somehow, this doesn't feel real.{何だか実感なくてさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.53,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Well... don't overdo it{FIRST AID!} either, okay?{まあ、無理もないよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.91,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's about time, I think.{そろそろかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:17.70,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke, let's go breathe a bit of the outside air.{恭介、ちょっと外の空気吸いに行こう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.33,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What business do we have at a place like the roof?{屋上なんかに何の用？}{pompf}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.88,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine.{いいからいいから}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.56,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Everybody!{みんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.72,Madoka,,0,0,0,,The real celebration is when you're discharged, but...{本当のお祝いは退院してからなんだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.07,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Your hands healed before your legs, you know.{足より先に手が治っちゃったしね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.41,Madoka,,0,0,0,,T–That's...{そ、それは}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.49,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You told me to dispose of it, but...{お前からは、処分してくれといわれていたが}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.20,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I couldn't throw it away.{どうしても棄てられなかったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.71,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I...{私は}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.56,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Now... please try it out. You don't have to be afraid.{さぁ、試したごらん。怖れなくっていい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.27,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mami-san...{\i0}{マミさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.94,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My wish... has been granted!{\i0}{あたしの願い、叶ったよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.82,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I'd have something like a regret.{\i0}{後悔なんて、あるわけない}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:16.24,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm... right now... the absolute happiest I can be!{\i0}{あたし、今最高に幸せだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.44,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's this town's new magical girl, huh?{あれがこの街の新しい魔法少女ねぇ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.44,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Do you really intend to conspire against her?{本当に彼女と事を構える気かい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.45,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't it too easy?{だってチョロそうじゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.70,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'll insta-kill that kind of person.{瞬殺っしょ、あんな奴}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.33,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Or what?{それとも何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.79,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Got a problem? You.{文句あるっての？アンタ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:09.46,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Everything is not limited to being as you plan.{すべて君の思い通りに行くとは限らないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.55,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Since there's one more magical girl in this city, you know.{この街にはもう一人、魔法少女がいるからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.22,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is that one?{何者なの？そいつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.76,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand that myself.{僕にもよく分からない}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.44,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hah?{はあ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.73,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?{どういうことさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:24.31,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Even they became a magical girl after forming a contract with you, right?{そいつだってアンタと契約して魔法少女になったんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.06,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You could say that's right, or you could say that's wrong.{そうとも言えるし、違うとも言える}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.88,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That girl is a guaranteed irregular.{あの子は極めつけのイレギュラーだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.00,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Even I can't predict what kind of actions she'll make.{どういう行動に出るか、僕にも予想できない}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.07,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hah! Isn't that perfect?{ハン！上等じゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.70,Madoka,,0,0,0,,After all, I dunno about too much boredom.{退屈過ぎてもなんだしさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.16,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Gotta have a little fun too, y'know...{ちっとは面白味もないとね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.46,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What did you want to discuss?{話って何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:58.47,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Um, well, it's just about Sayaka-chan, but...{あのね、さやかちゃんのこと、なんだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:04.61,Madoka,,0,0,0,,T–That girl, you know... vehemently makes an assumption, is really stubborn, and then—{あ、あの子はね、思い込みが激しくて、意地っ張りで}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:07.02,Madoka,,0,0,0,,She gets into fights with people fairly quickly...{結構すぐ人と喧嘩しちゃったり}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.98,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But you know, she's a really good girl!{でもね、すっごくいい子なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,She's kind, and has courage.{優しくて勇気があって}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.74,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If she's thinking in another person's interest, she'll really keep at it...{誰かのためと思ったらがんばり過ぎちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.78,Madoka,,0,0,0,,For a magical girl, that's fatal, you know.{魔法少女としては、致命的ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.78,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Is that... so?{そう……なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:24.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Extreme kindness is connected to naïveté.{度を越した優しさは、甘さにつながるし}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.99,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Reckless courage becomes negligence.{蛮勇は油断になる}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:30.00,Madoka,,0,0,0,,And... no matter how much dedication you have, there's nothing like a reward.{そして、どんな献身にも見返りなんてない}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:34.75,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand that, you aren't fit to be a magical girl.{それをわきまえていなければ、魔法少女は務まらない}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.42,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's why Tomoe Mami lost her life.{だから巴マミも命を落とした}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.80,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Stop talking like that!{そんな言い方やめてよっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:49.30,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Right... even though Sayaka-chan herself says that she's fine...{そう、さやかちゃん、自分では平気だって言ってるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:54.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Still, when I think about the possibility of something similar to that time with Mami-san occurring,{でも、もしマミさんの時と同じようなことになったらって思うと}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.36,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I... what should I do?{私どうすればいいのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.82,Madoka,,0,0,0,,So you're worried about Miki Sayaka, then.{美樹さやかのことが心配なのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:05.57,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I... can't give Sayaka-chan strength anymore, so...{私じゃもう、さやかちゃんの力にはなってあげられないから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.79,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to ask it of you, Homura-chan.{だから、ほむらちゃんにお願いしたいの}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Please get along with Sayaka-chan.{さやかちゃんと仲良くしてあげて}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.00,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Don't fight with her like you did those times with Mami-san!{マミさんの時みたいに喧嘩しないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:20.55,Madoka,,0,0,0,,During the times when you attack witches too, it should be much safer if everyone cooperates by fighting together, you know!{魔女をやっつける時も、みんなで協力して戦えば、ずっと安全なはずだよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.97,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell lies.{私は嘘をつきたくないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.94,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make promises I'm unable to keep, either.{出来もしない約束もしたくない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.77,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Therefore... give up on Miki Sayaka.{だから、美樹さやかのことは諦めて}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.42,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Why...{どうしてなの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.38,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That girl shouldn't have contracted.{あの子は契約すべきじゃなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.54,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Certainly, it was my miss.{確かに私のミスよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:53.50,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Instead of just you, I should have kept precise observation on her as well.{貴女だけでなく、彼女もきちんと監視しておくべきだった}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.37,Madoka,,0,0,0,,In that case—{なら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.54,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But, after admitting responsibility, let me say something.{でも、責任を認めた上で言わせて貰うわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:03.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's a miss that cannot be redeemed by any means.{今となっては、どうやっても償いきれないミスなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:06.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing as how someone who has died is unable to return.{死んでしまった人が還って来ないのと同じこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.01,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Once you become a magical girl,{一度魔法少女になってしまった}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.68,Madoka,,0,0,0,,there's nothing like hope for salvation anymore.{もう救われる望みなんてない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:19.19,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That contract means giving up on everything in exchange for just a single hope, after all.{あの契約は、たった一つの希望と引き換えに、すべてを諦めるってことだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:24.38,Madoka,,0,0,0,,So, you've also given up, Homura-chan?{だから、ほむらちゃんも諦めちゃってるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.91,Madoka,,0,0,0,,On yourself, and the other girls too... everything?{自分のことも、他の子のことも全部}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.33,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yes.{ええ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.54,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I won't make an excuse by saying this is atonement or something.{罪滅ぼしなんて言い訳はしないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:38.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I will continue my fight, regardless of what kind of sins I have to commit.{私はどんな罪を背負おうと私の戦いを続けなきゃならない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.93,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I wasted your time, didn't I?{時間を無駄にさせたわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.80,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I am sorry.{ごめんなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.44,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Are you nervous?{緊張してるのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:06.93,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I guess.{まあね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:09.45,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'm done for if I make a single mistake, after all.{一つ間違えたらお陀仏なわけだし}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.28,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Madoka?{まどか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:18.54,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan, from here on, are you...{さやかちゃん、これから、その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.84,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yup. I'm going on patrol to search for bad witches!{そう、悪い魔女を探してパトロール}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.96,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Since this is another duty of an ally of justice, you know.{これも正義の味方の勤めだからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.47,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine... all by yourself?{一人で…平気なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.10,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I'm fine!{平気平気}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:31.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Even Mami-san had to go and do this.{マミさんだってそうして来たんだし}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.22,Madoka,,0,0,0,,As her {\i1}kouhai{\i0}, this is expected of me.{後輩として、それぐらいはね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:37.10,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Um, you know... I... can't do anything,{あのね、私、何もできないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.98,Madoka,,0,0,0,,and even though I understand that I'll just get in your way...{足手まといにしかならないってわかってるんだけど}{noted on site}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:40.98,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Still...{でも、}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.23,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's fine if it's only while I'm not a burden,{邪魔にならないところまででいいの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.99,Madoka,,0,0,0,,until then, if we go together—{行けるところまで一緒に連れてってもらえたらって}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.49,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Aren't you trying too hard?{頑張り過ぎじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.44,Madoka,,0,0,0,,S–Sorry...{ご、ごめん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:58.13,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's no good, right? I understand that I'm just a bother...{ダメだよね、迷惑だってのはわかってたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.25,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No, I'm really happy!{ううん。すっごく嬉しい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.84,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you figure it out?{ねえ分かる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:07.38,Madoka,,0,0,0,,My hands started shaking earlier... and they haven't stopped.{手が震えちゃってさ。さっきから止まらないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Pitiful, isn't it?{情けないよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:13.39,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm already a magical girl, it's like I'm disheartened when I'm alone.{もう魔法少女だってのに、一人だと心細いなんてさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.22,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan...{さやかちゃん……}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:18.10,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You aren't anything like a nuisance. I'm really happy.{邪魔なんかじゃない。すごく嬉しい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.97,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Just being with someone is really heartening.{誰かが一緒にいてくれるだけで、すっごく心強いよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.48,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have the strength of a hundred people.{それこそ百人力って感じ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.73,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I...{私}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.10,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you without fail.{必ず守るよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:30.36,Madoka,,0,0,0,,So be at ease, and follow behind me.{だから安心して私の後についてきて}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:33.16,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Let's beat those witches together, like we've done up until now!{今まで見たいに、一緒に魔女をやっつけよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:33.91,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.87,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You're aware of the danger, right?{危険は承知の上なんだね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:43.50,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Since I'm an idiot, I might do something reckless if I'm alone.{あたしバカだから、一人だと無茶なでたらめやらかしかねないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:48.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,When I take to heart that even Madoka is here, I believe that alone will make me more cautious.{まどかもいるんだって肝に銘じてれば、それだけ慎重になれると思う}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I see.{そうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.63,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's fine if you've thought about it.{うん、考えがあっての事ならいいんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.68,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Kyubey...{QB}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:58.18,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}You've also had your own thoughts about this, right, Madoka?{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{君にも君の考えがあるんだろう？　まどか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:02.35,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}I understand your feelings of wanting to protect Sayaka.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{さやかを守りたい君の気持ちは分かる}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:05.15,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}In reality, just by staying next to her,{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{実際、君が隣に居てくれるだけで}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.82,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}you possess a single trump card that's ready to be used in the worst-case scenario, don't you?{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{最悪の事態に備えた切り札を一つだけ用意できるしね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.07,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}I...{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{私は}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.12,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}You don't have to say anything right now.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{今は何も言わなくていい}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Sayaka will surely object to it too, I believe.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{さやかもきっと反対するだろうし}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:26.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Just... if there comes a time when you've made up your mind, then my preparations will always be in order, okay?{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{ただ、もし君が心を決める時が来たら、僕の準備は、いつでも整ってるからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.00,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Yeah.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.26,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's here.{ここだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:45.27,Madoka,,0,0,0,,This barrier probably isn't a witch's, but instead belongs to a familiar.{この結界は、多分魔女じゃなくて使い魔のものだね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.90,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I can't get comfortable.{楽に越した事ないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.78,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'm still a beginner, after all.{こちとらまだ初心者なんだし}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.65,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Unpreparedness is a forbidden thing.{油断は禁物だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.15,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I understand that!{分かってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.37,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's...{あれが}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's running away!{逃げるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:05.87,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!{任せて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:37.20,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hold it, hold it. What are you girls doing, exactly?{ちょっとちょっと。何やってんのさ、アンタたち}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.20,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It'll get away!{逃がしちゃう}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.25,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell by looking?{見てわかんないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.60,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's not a witch, it's a familiar.{ありゃ魔女じゃなくて使い魔だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.88,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It's not carrying a Grief Seed, is it?{グリーフシードを持ってるわけないじゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.46,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But, if you leave it alone, won't it kill someone?{だって、あれほっといたら誰かが殺されるのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.22,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's why, like...{だからさぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:01.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You have to wait for it eat four or five people and become a witch.{４～５人ばかり食って魔女になるまで待てっての}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:04.60,Madoka,,0,0,0,,'Cause that way it'll conceive a proper Grief Seed, y'know.{そうすりゃちゃんとグリーフシードも孕むんだからさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.56,Madoka,,0,0,0,,What're you going to do when you strangle a chicken before it lays eggs, huh?{アンタ、卵産む前の鶏シメてどうすんのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:14.07,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we should watch as the people attacked by witches helplessly die!?{魔女に襲われる人たちを…あんた、見殺しにするって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Aren't you, like, having some kind of major misunderstanding?{アンタさぁ、何か大元から勘違いしてんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.12,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Do you know about the food chain?{食物連鎖って知ってる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.83,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You learned it in school, yeah?{学校で習ったよねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.00,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Weak humans are eaten by witches.{弱い人間を魔女が食う}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.58,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Those witches are eaten by us.{その魔女をアタシたちが食う}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.00,Madoka,,0,0,0,,This is an obvious rule, right?{これが当たり前のルールでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,'Cause it just goes in order of strength, after all.{そういう強さの順番なんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.13,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's...{そんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:40.64,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You're...{あんたは}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.73,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's possible, but...{まさかとは思うけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:47.48,Madoka,,0,0,0,,For the sake of forcing a joke so flashy as "helping other people in the name of justice"...{やれ人助けだの正義だの、その手のおチャラケた冗談かますために}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:52.81,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That couldn't be the reason a contract was formed with that thing, right? You.{アイツと契約したわけじゃないよね？アンタ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.65,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If it was, what would you say!?{だったら、何だって言うのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:03.49,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hey now, could you stop?{ちょっとさ、やめてくれない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:19.22,Madoka,,0,0,0,,When you stick your neck into my work, half just for fun, y'know... it seriously pisses me off.{遊び半分で首突っ込まれるのってさ、ホントムカつくんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.73,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan!{さやかちゃん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.06,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Newbie...{ふんっ！トーシロが。}{Check site notes}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.11,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Cool your head a little bit.{ちっとは頭冷やせっての}{before nanoha tells you to instead}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.95,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's strange.{おっかしいなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:44.99,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Full recovery should take about 3 months after that, but...{全治３ヶ月ってぐらいにはかましてやったはずなんだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.58,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan's fine?{さやかちゃん、平気なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.62,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's because she became a magical girl with a prayer for healing.{彼女は癒しの祈りを契約にして魔法少女になったからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.71,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Her damage resilience is higher than other people's.{ダメージの回復力は人一倍だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.21,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Who'd... to someone like you...{誰が…あんたなんかに}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:02.22,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Since there are people like you... Mami-san is...{あんたみたいな奴がいるから、マミさんは…！！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:03.72,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Annoying.{ウゼェ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.68,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Super annoying!{超ウゼェ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:13.18,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Actually, what? I don't want to hear you talking like that in the first place, y'know.{つうか何。そもそも口の利き方がなってないよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.06,Madoka,,0,0,0,,In front of your {\i1}senpai{\i0}.{先輩に向かってさぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.44,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Silence!{黙れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:24.11,Madoka,,0,0,0,,We aren't messing around by dancing, y'know! Fool!{チャラチャラ踊ってんじゃねぇよウスノロ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan!{さやかちゃん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.04,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Madoka, it's dangerous if you get any closer!{まどか、近づいたら危険だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.54,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand when I tell you,{言って聞かせてわからねえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.30,Madoka,,0,0,0,,and you're an idiot that doesn't understand when I beat it into you, either...{殴ってもわからねえバカとなりゃあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.80,Madoka,,0,0,0,,After that, nothing left but killing ya, y'know!{後は殺しちゃうしかないよねッ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.56,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I won't lose...{負けない}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.31,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You think I'd lose!?{負けるもんかあ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:11.54,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Why...?{どうして？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.09,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hey, why?{ね、どうして？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:18.29,Madoka,,0,0,0,,She isn't a witch, so why do fellow allies have to fight?{魔女じゃないのに。どうして味方同士で戦わなきゃならないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.45,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Nothing can be done.{どうしようもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.63,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Neither of them wants to do anything like surrender.{お互い譲る気なんてまるでないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.78,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Please, Kyubey! Make them stop!{お願い、キュゥべえ。やめさせて}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.17,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Such a thing shouldn't be happening!{こんなのってないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:30.97,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything.{僕にはどうしようもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:31.39,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But...{でも}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:36.81,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If you want to stop them by force no matter what, then it's not like there aren't any methods.{どうしても力づくでも止めたいのなら、方法がないわけじゃないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.32,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No one besides another magical girl can thrust themselves into this battle.{この戦いに割り込むには、同じ魔法少女じゃなきゃダメだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:45.24,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But if it's you, you have those qualifications.{でも君にならその資格がある}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.82,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If that's what you truly desire, you know.{本当にそれを望むならね}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.24,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}{そうだ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.33,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I contract...{\i0}{私が契約すれば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:56.16,Madoka,,0,0,0,,This is the end!{終わりだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:03.30,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}{私…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That is now unnecessary.{それには及ばないわ}
